node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 16, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'OVERTHINKING WILL STEAL YOUR PEACE AND SLEEP. PRAY AND LEAVE IT IN GOD'S HANDS.'.

node.text: I decree that you begin to  experience restful sleep like never before. In Jesus name, I break the power of restlessness, sleeplessness, insomnia, tensions, and physical distress that would rob you of a good nights rest. I cast out every nightmare and night terror and I say it cannot operate ever again around you or your home! I speak peace to your mind and body during the night hours. I say that every muscle, bone, sale, organ and hormone must align itself correctly so you are able to rest. I speak peace to the environment around you and say that you operate in God’s promise that he gives his beloved sleep. I speak Sweet sleep upon you and may your nights be restful, comfortable, relaxing, and calm. I say that your nights of sleep shall be the best and most rejuvenating yet! Amen

This WEEK be determined to MOVE UP and FORWARD! How do you do that? Release yourself from ALL shame, pain and stress! You got this!! Let’s go! This week is your week for breakthroughs! Brethren, I count not myself to have apprehended: but this one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind, and reaching forth unto those things which are before, 14. I press toward the mark for the prize of the high calling of God in Christ Jesus. 
Phil 3:13-14
